---
// Services.astro — 3 alternating service blocks with gradient image placeholders
---

<section id="servicios" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color: #B97333;">
        Lo que ofrecemos
      </span>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-4"
        style="color: #0B1B32; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        data-i18n="services.title"
      >Nuestros Servicios</h2>
      <p
        class="text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        style="color: #8E9297;"
        data-i18n="services.subtitle"
      >Gestión integral de RAEE con destrucción de datos certificada, trazabilidad auditable y cumplimiento REP, todo en un solo socio.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 1: Image Left / Text Right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
      <!-- Image (left) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-left">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Recolección y logística de residuos electrónicos"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(11,27,50,0.4) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text (right) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-right">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-wide"
            style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.1); color: #B97333;"
          >
            <span>01</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Data destruction highlight badge -->
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full"
            style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.12); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.25);"
          >
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
            Destrucción de datos incluida
          </span>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4"
          style="color: #0B1B32; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          data-i18n="services.items.0.title"
        >Recolección, Logística y Destrucción de Datos</h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4"
          style="color: #8E9297;"
          data-i18n="services.items.0.desc"
        >Retiro programado en tu empresa con flota propia y manifiestos certificados. Cada dispositivo recibe borrado seguro o destrucción física del soporte, con certificado individual por número de serie, válido para auditorías de cumplimiento normativo.</p>
        <!-- Feature pills -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #F4F4F4; color: #8E9297;">Acta de recepción inmediata</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #F4F4F4; color: #8E9297;">Cert. por dispositivo</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #F4F4F4; color: #8E9297;">Respuesta en 24h</span>
        </div>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold transition-colors duration-200 group"
          style="color: #B97333;"
          data-i18n="services.items.0.cta"
        >
          Agenda un retiro
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2: Text Left / Image Right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
      <!-- Image (right on desktop, top on mobile) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-right">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Tratamiento y valorización de componentes electrónicos"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(11,27,50,0.4) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text (left on desktop) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-left">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 tracking-wide"
          style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.1); color: #B97333;"
        >
          <span>02</span>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4"
          style="color: #0B1B32; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          data-i18n="services.items.1.title"
        >Tratamiento y Valorización</h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-6"
          style="color: #8E9297;"
          data-i18n="services.items.1.desc"
        >Desmantelamiento, clasificación y procesamiento de residuos electrónicos con recuperación de metales preciosos y materiales reutilizables. Los materiales regresan al ciclo productivo como materia prima secundaria.</p>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold transition-colors duration-200 group"
          style="color: #B97333;"
          data-i18n="services.items.1.cta"
        >
          Más información
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 3: Image Left / Text Right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Image (left) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-left">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Gestión REP y reportería de cumplimiento normativo"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(11,27,50,0.4) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text (right) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 reveal-right">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 tracking-wide"
          style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.1); color: #B97333;"
        >
          <span>03</span>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4"
          style="color: #0B1B32; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          data-i18n="services.items.2.title"
        >Gestión REP y Reportería</h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-6"
          style="color: #8E9297;"
          data-i18n="services.items.2.desc"
        >Administramos tu obligación REP como productor: desde la inscripción en el registro hasta los informes anuales al Ministerio del Medio Ambiente. Simplificamos tu cumplimiento normativo.</p>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold transition-colors duration-200 group"
          style="color: #B97333;"
          data-i18n="services.items.2.cta"
        >
          Más información
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
